![](data:image/png;base64,)

This panel allows to configure the processing of electronic invoices specific to the Italian public administration.

**Option**

**Description**

**Fattura PA Document Name**

Shipment attribute that contains the reference to the PA invoice. The drop-down menu shows all the attributes of the shipment selector as defined in the data schema.

**No Attachment**

The input data will be digitally signed, but no attachment will be generated or included.

**Produce or Normalize Attachment**

The input data will be digitally signed and attachments will be created using Document Composition or the spool normalization module.

**Description **: Name of the attribute of the input document that contains the attachment content description, used for signing.

**External Attachment**

The input data will be signed and the existing documents will be attached. The attachments will not be created by DC/OM, in the current run, but by an external system before starting DC/OM.

- **Name**: Name of the attribute of the input document that defines the attachment name, used for signing. 

- **Compression**: Attribute of the input document that contains the compression algorithm, used for signing.

- **Format**: Attribute of the input document that contains the attachment format, used for signing .

- **Description**: Attribute of the input document that contains the attachment content description, used for signing.
